graph TD
    SDK[SDK] -->|Archives & Deploys| Platform[Platform]
    Platform -->|Deploys Container| CICD[CI/CD Service]
    CICD -->|Spins up| GV[Gvisor Service]
    Platform <-->|Communicates via Protocol| MCP[MCP Server]
    MCP -->|Loads Runtime Components from| Workspace
    
    subgraph SDK_Contains["SDK Contains"]
        subgraph agentic_core["agentic-core library"]
            Models[Designtime Models]
            AgentProtocol[Runtime AgentProtocol]
            PlatformAPI[Platform API]
        end
        subgraph Workspace
            DesignTime[Design Time Code]
            RuntimeCode[Runtime Code]
            CLITools[CLI Tools]
            BuildScripts[Build Scripts]
        end
    end

    subgraph Platform_Components["Platform Components"]
        subgraph API["Platform API"]
            DeployAPI[Deploy API]
            UndeployAPI[Undeploy API]
            ExecuteAPI[Execute API]
        end
        subgraph MCP_Integration["MCP Integration"]
            MCPClient[MCP Client]
            ToolDiscovery[Tool Discovery]
            ToolExecution[Tool Execution]
        end
        subgraph Gvisor_Service["Gvisor Service"]
            ContainerLifecycle[Container Lifecycle]
            HealthMonitor[Health Monitoring]
            K8sProvision[K8s Provisioning]
        end
    end

    subgraph Runtime["Runtime Environment"]
        subgraph MCP_Components["MCP Components"]
            CustomTools[Custom Tools]
            CustomOrchestrator[Custom Orchestrator]
            RuntimeEnv[Runtime Environment]
        end
    end

    %% Interactions
    SDK -->|Archive| DeployAPI
    SDK -->|Deploy| DeployAPI
    SDK -->|Undeploy| UndeployAPI
    SDK -->|Test| ExecuteAPI
    
    DeployAPI -->|Trigger| CICD
    CICD -->|Provision| GV
    GV -->|Start| MCP
    
    MCPClient -->|Connect| MCP
    MCPClient -->|Discover| ToolDiscovery
    MCPClient -->|Execute| ToolExecution
    
    MCP -->|Register| CustomTools
    MCP -->|Register| CustomOrchestrator
    
    %% Environment Configurations
    subgraph Environments["Environments"]
        Dev[Development]
        Staging[Staging]
        Prod[Production]
    end
    
    SDK -->|Configure| Environments
